<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>The truth about whiners.</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Hawthorne">Hawthorne</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 9:11 a.m. 19/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> The truth about whiners.<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1544" TARGET=_self>The Truth About PVP Roleplaying</A> (The RealmWeaver)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>PvP isnt about role-playing, sure we role-play to an extenet, but not to the extent of the other servers. Why? Because its how we choose to play. Thats why 989 made the PvP shard. To accomodate what you as a true role-player do not like.

<P>So good for you, go play on your other servers. But when you get bored with hack and slash monster bash you will understand what PvP is all about. Then you may even build up some rivalries and say things like "shit, im gonna beat your ass". But no no no. Your a role-player.. Again you wouldnt understand.
<P>Some of my best friends used to hate me. And yea, its a power trip. Its a game.. Its how I prefer to play it. Cant handle it? Go back to UO.
<P>Hawthorne, The Regulators.
<BR>www.theregulators.org
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
